author: Anjana George
title: Dulquer supports Anna Katharina's new single
text:
Mollwyood's young heartthrob, Dulquer Salmaan, who is known for supporting his friends in their every venture, came forward to launch the first single of Anna Katherina.
Actor took his Facebook page to express his favor to the Appangalembadum singer. He wrote, "Had a wonderful evening at Anna's launch of her new album 'Honey Bee' ! I've known her from Ustaad hotel days and she's always been a close friend and a strong supporter of my work. It was lovely meeting your whole family and your huge group of friends, Anna. Wishing you all success. Here is the link to her awesome new music video you guys ! Enjoy. (Sic)"
The single titled as Honeybee is said to be a musical story teller and talks about the innocence of childhood.
